QuestData.Title: Unbound Darkness
QuestData.Description: <The sound of chimes enters your head, but it is distressed.>$B$BWe imprisoned the most dangerous beings we came across in our travels.$B$BZereketh is a powerful void lord. If he escapes into Netherstorm, he will feed off of the abundant void energy.
QuestData.PortraitGiverText: None of the prisoners may be allowed to escape.
QuestData.PortraitTurnInText: Unfortunately, yet more dangerous inmates have escaped.
QuestData.LogDescription: A'dal has asked you to slay Zereketh the Unbound in the Arcatraz of Tempest Keep.
QuestData.RewardText: Creatures of the void are naturally chaotic. They are a necessary part of the universe, but they must be kept in check by the Light.
